title: Milestones & Mentions - Mana Qulqullummaa Orbital
heading: Milestones & Mentions
description: Hojiin aartii waggoota hedduudhaaf hojjetame kun qaama Bienaal Mercosul 13ffaa Biraazil, Porto Alegre keessatti gaggeeffame yoo ta'u, kan Marcelo Dantas'n qophaa'edha. Badhaasa Lumen Prize 2022 - Futures Award jedhamuuf tarree dheeraa keessa galeera. Akkasumas dorgommii CubeDesign 2021 kan Inistiitiyuutii Qorannoo Hawaa Biraazil (INPE)n guddifame ArtSat Category injifateera.
